reviewText: Beautiful movie and history of the Bandoneon
A one of a kind. Wonderful story and passion. If I did not know it, I would say it was a drama not a documentary.

First rate, Thank you Moviemars for getting this DVD to me, despite an out of stock problem, it only tok a few more days for you guys to come through. We watched the movie last night and thoroughly enjoyed it. I am not a big DVD watcher but would definitly order again from Moviemars when I next want a DVD.
